{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "阿尔贝里亚骑士道 新的骑士道",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "二人成功退敌并与白燕骑士团会合。\\n利弗再次劝赛希尔与他同回圣城，\\n但赛希尔以需要思考自己的骑士道为由拒绝。\\n利弗接受了赛希尔找到的答案，\\n并在相约再会后与她告别。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "哈尔！\\n你休想再胡作非为！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "哼……呵呵呵……你这个老好人\\n竟然能毫不犹豫地下手……呃啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "这才叫看在同窗的份上……\\n你就死个痛快吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "呃啊！\\n呃，唔唔唔……哈哈哈哈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "他明明受了致命伤，\\n还在笑？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "致命伤？\\n你是说这点小伤吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "伤口，正逐渐愈合！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "啊……好像有点玩过头了，\\n竟然要动用这份力量……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "很遗憾，游戏到此为止。\\n在我的夙愿即将达成之际，\\n岂能功亏一篑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "愿伟大之主降临——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "站住，哈尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "利弗，不行！\\n碰到瘴气会有危险！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "那么诸位，我就此告辞。\\n有缘再会吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "消失了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "那是……什么力量啊？\\n难以想象是人类的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "哈尔身上发生了什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（哈尔志在谋求平等的世界，\\n所以他对君主毫无忠心可言。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（他这种人所敬仰的“主”，\\n到底是……还有那瘴气又是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "白燕骑士团团员们",
            "context": "利弗团长，您没事吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "抱歉让你们担心了。\\n感谢你们前来营救。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗雷德",
            "context": "趁格拉姆斯那帮人追过来之前，\\n我们赶紧越过边境吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "嗯。\\n赛希尔，你呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "诶……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "就算知道了你的秘密，\\n我的想法也没有变。\\n和我一起来新阿尔贝里亚吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我很理解你的内疚\\n还有悔恨。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "所以才希望能作为伙伴\\n帮你分担一点重负。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "唔啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔！？\\n哪里受伤了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "不是……我要……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "要？\\n要什么？要魔养石吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "不是……我要……\\n要被你闪瞎了……\\n你也太耀眼了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "哈哈哈，这样啊。\\n不过你就忍忍吧，因为这就是——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "你的“真实想法”，对吧？\\n我知道啦……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我很高兴你有这份心意，\\n但是——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我还是想自己一个人再想想，\\n什么才是属于自己的骑士道。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我一定无法再走上过去那条路了……\\n毕竟我没能保护好王已成事实。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "而且……为此牺牲了\\n无辜的民众和龙也是事实。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "基于这些，我想我必须找到\\n自己今后要走的路。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "这样啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "而、而且……我现在站在你身旁，\\n怎么说呢……还是会难过……\\n应该说内心还难以承受……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "那个……说白了就是，\\n你太耀眼了，\\n我在旁边都快融化了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "哈哈，融化了可就麻烦了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "对吧？\\n不过呢——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我觉得，要是能再次和你\\n一同为阿尔贝里亚而战……\\n也挺不错的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我知道了……\\n那我等着你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "等你有朝一日找到自己的骑士道，\\n再与我共赴战场。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "嗯……谢谢你……\\n回去的路上要小心啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "嗯，你也保重。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120126_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "白燕骑士团团员们",
            "context": "利弗团长，她究竟是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "她曾是阿尔贝里亚的骑士，\\n同时也永远是……\\n我的伙伴。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（赛希尔……我相信你。\\n我们一定还会再会。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我没法再回格拉姆斯了……\\n所以老板娘就拜托你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120043_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "嗯，这回我不会大意了，\\n会把她平安送回格拉姆斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "多谢……\\n抱歉连累了你们两位。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "老板娘",
            "context": "别在意。我还近距离看到了\\n你威风帅气的一面呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "诶？威风帅气……哪、哪里啊？\\n我总是惊慌失措的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "老板娘",
            "context": "说什么呢。\\n你不是拼命保护了我们吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120043_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "那时候的你，\\n真是最帅气的骑士！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "老板娘",
            "context": "即使相隔两地，我也会支持你的。\\n加油啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "好……\\n那你们多保重。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（没想到我竟然……\\n会想要从头再来。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "“第十戒 骑士者当行正义与善，\\n时刻和不端与恶做斗争。”",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "虽然不知道新的骑士道\\n会是什么样的一条道路……\\n但我不会再迷失自我了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110394_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "因为……正义就在我心中。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_06_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}